lunchr

Send lunch menu via SMS to subscribers.

REQUIREMENTS:
 * Python 2.6+
 * html5lib
 * py-dom-xpath
 * Account with mo-sms.com

INSTALLATION:
sudo easy_install html5lib
sudo easy_install py-dom-xpath

